# Test 15: Fibonacci sequence
Create a function called fibonacci that takes n:
    If n is less than 2, then:
        Return n.
    End if.
    Set a to 0.
    Set b to 1.
    For i from 2 to n, do:
        Set temp to a plus b.
        Set a to b.
        Set b to temp.
    End for.
    Return b.
End function.

Show "Fibonacci sequence (first 10):".
For i from 0 to 9, do:
    Set fib to call fibonacci with i.
    Show "fib(" plus i plus ") = " plus fib.
End for.
